## Quick Commands
```bash
# Data Collection
python main.py                          # Run collectors
python check_status.py                  # System status

# API Server
venv\Scripts\activate                   # Activate venv
python api_server.py                    # Start API
python test_api.py                      # Test endpoints

# URLs
http://localhost:8000                   # API Base
http://localhost:8000/api/docs          # Swagger UI
```

